nodes.text: R-Duba was a desert and ocean planet located in the R-Duba system, within the Quiberon sector of the galaxy's Outer Rim Territories. A minor trade world, it was located in a backwater province of the Galactic Empire.

R-Duba first appeared in Droids 5, the fifth issue of the Star Wars Legends Star Wars: Droids comic series published by Star Comics, an imprint of Marvel Comics, which was first published on December 1, 1986.
